00:00:01,478 --> 00:00:04,987
I used to be absolutely terrified of public speaking

2
00:00:04,987 --> 00:00:07,401
much more than you are or you were.

3
00:00:07,401 --> 00:00:09,983
And it really held me back in my career

4
00:00:09,983 --> 00:00:11,634
for a lot of my life.

5
00:00:11,634 --> 00:00:14,200
I actually remember in business school

6
00:00:14,200 --> 00:00:16,731
