16
00:00:47,421 --> 00:00:50,226
And I eventually realized that you really

17
00:00:50,226 --> 00:00:54,391
can't achieve all of your goals in life if you can't

18
00:00:54,391 --> 00:00:57,997
confront your fears and master public speaking.

19
00:00:57,997 --> 00:00:59,707
