63
00:02:56,389 --> 00:03:00,415
those poor kids that were incarcerated.

64
00:03:00,415 --> 00:03:04,197
I wanted to teach them life skills and mentorship

65
00:03:04,197 --> 00:03:07,640
and really inspire them to turn their lives around.

66
00:03:07,640 --> 00:03:10,550
Right, it's never too late.

67
00:03:10,550 --> 00:03:14,239
I was only supposed to present to a couple inmates

68
00:03:14,239 --> 00:03:17,504
at a time, and they gave me a police pass.

69
00:03:17,504 --> 00:03:19,132
