129
00:05:58,324 --> 00:06:00,320
And that could have been me if I was caught

130
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:02,917
at the wrong time in my life.

131
00:06:02,917 --> 00:06:05,407
And so I read that the pamphlet, right,

132
00:06:05,407 --> 00:06:07,884
they give me a pamphlet that was given by the church.

133
00:06:07,884 --> 00:06:11,433
Remember the priest wasn't there so I had to fill in.

134
00:06:11,433 --> 00:06:16,265
And that particular gospel passage that I read from

135
00:06:16,265 --> 00:06:20,141
