184
00:08:53,771 --> 00:08:57,771
and that I had that revelation and sense of love

185
00:08:59,025 --> 00:09:02,662
and humbly empowering the empowerers events

186
00:09:02,662 --> 00:09:04,745
occur earlier in my life.

